subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: No. 14 Maria Sharapova, who won the Australian Open in 2008, lost her first-round match in Melbourne to her fellow Russian Maria Kirilenko, 7-6 (4), 3-6, 6-4.
